aV[Surgery]
p135
aa(lp136
VThe follow-up MRIs showed, luckily, little to no growth of the cancer.
p137
aVSo I was able to take my time and choose.
p138
aVI chose the doctor I wanted to work with,
p139
aVI chose the hospital I wanted to stay in,
p140
aVand in the meanwhile, I was supported by thousands of people,
p141
aVnone of whom felt pity for me.
p142
aVEveryone felt like they could take an active role
p143
aVin helping me to get well,
p144
aVand this was the most important part of La Cura.
